ggplot2 0.8.8 (2010-XX-XX) ----------------------------------------

* statistics now also respect layer parameter inherit.aes (thanks to bug report by Lorenzo Isella and investigation by Brian Diggs)
* fix ordering bug in facet_wrap (thanks to bug report by Frank Davenport)
* geom_hline and geom_vline will not impact legend when used for fixed intercepts
* panels with no non-missing values trigged errors with some statistics. (reported by Giovanni Dall'Olio)
* check all axis labels for expressions (reported by Benji Oswald)
* geom_errobarh now respects height parameter
* stat_smooth now uses built-in confidence interval (with small sample correction) for linear models (thanks to suggestion by Ian Fellows)